                  "id": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3ft8f52x/manifest/annotation/p2",
                  "type": "Annotation",
                  "motivation": "commenting",
                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p>has been established, is natural; but remember it<lb/> is not with your <add>ומבן\n                    חמישים שנה ישוב מצבאות העבודה</add>, but <add>ומבן ששים</add>. You can\n                without<lb/> desertions the holy cause still <sic>fulfil</sic> the command,\n                    <add>ושרת את אחיו באהל מועד</add><lb/>\n                <add>לא אמות כי אחיה וגו'</add>, and be as useful as ever, tho the locality<lb/> be\n                smaller. You have <hi rend=\"underline\">earned</hi> your <hi rend=\"underline\"\n                        ><sic>olium</sic></hi>, and if you<lb/> can enjoy it <add>?</add>, why not\n                avail yourself<lb/> of so seasonable an opportunity, in the society of those<lb/>\n                who would hail your coming with enthusiasm, and in<lb/> a climate more genial to\n                your partly worn out constitution,<lb/> enfeebled by excessive work in the cause of\n                your people.<lb/> I think you ought, and so will every true friend of yours.<lb/> We\n                don't want you to drop at your post from sheer fatigue;<lb/> say then to us <add>במה\n                    מדליקין</add>, and accept the post.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">Orthodoxy, from the stand-point, I view it, cannot long<lb/>\n                maintain its ground in <placeName>America</placeName>, nor elsewhere concessions<lb/>\n                <hi rend=\"underline\">must</hi> be made; not in the homeopathic doses you wish<lb/>\n                to administer, but in heroic quantities, as the M Dr<lb/> say <add>קדיש</add> and a\n                    <add>שומרים</add> are not enough, and as <persName>Mr Moïse</persName><lb/>\n                justly observes if you concede <hi rend=\"underline\">them</hi>, the precedent is<lb/>\n                at once established for granting more. You have fought<lb/> a good fight, but\n                overwhelming odds are against you.</p>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3ft8f52x/canvas/p2"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
