                  "motivation": "commenting",
                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p>is in every house, and every one of my pupils is furnished<lb/> with it. Every Jewish\n                child in school, for I have many<lb/> Christian pupils too, learn, to translate\n                Bible and prayer<lb/> Book. So you see, tho' we are far from the great<lb/> centres\n                of enlightenment, and tho' I am as rusty as an<lb/> old door nail, we can compare,\n                as a Congregation,<lb/> with the best, and not be ashamed. It would do your<lb/>\n                heart good to witness the solemnity and decorum of our<lb/> worship. On <add>חמש\n                    מגילות</add> we began at 8 and tho' nothing was<lb/> omitted as laid down in the\n                old Portuguese sidder<add>?</add><lb/> we finished at 11. <date>Kippoor</date> we\n                began at 6, and at 6<lb/> P.M. I dismissed the congregation. I do not allow<lb/> the\n                Shophar to be blown till the whole of the <add>ודי לצרה בשעתה</add> is<lb/>\n                finished, whereby much confusion and indecency are<lb/> avoided. For men I to have\n                it sounded before <add>Hebrew</add><lb/> there would be a rush to leave, by which\n                the whole affect<lb/> of the day would be destroyed.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">i have written you, not one megillah but<lb/>\n                <add>Hebrew</add>, so I defer writing more <add>Hebrew</add>. I hope to<lb/> hear\n                that your health is good, in which my dear wife<lb/> heartily joins—and with regards\n                to your nieces, and<lb/> remembrances to inquiring friends, and many years of<lb/>\n                happiness and comfort I am</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(12)\">yours sincerely</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(12)\">\n                <persName role=\"author\">M N Nathan</persName>\n            </p>\n        </body>\n    </text>\n</TEI>"
                  },
